			<text><![CDATA[I declare under oath that I have personally accomplished this Personal Data Sheet which is a true, correct and
complete statement pursuant to the provisions of pertinent laws, rules and regulations of the Republic of the
Philippines. I authorize the agency head/authorized representative to verify tghe contents stated herein.
I agree that any misrepresentation made in this document and its attachments shall cause the filing of
administrative/criminal case/s against me.]]></text>
